          <div class="col-sm-7">
            <h4 class="i18n">{{_t "Get everyone prepared for a successful meeting" }}</h4>
            <p class="i18n">{{_t "Solid automatically retrieves all your agenda information from your Google Calendar. Your present and future events are analyzed, allowing you to receive instant notifications on the meetings that are not « solid » enough to be held." }}</p>
          </div>
