          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="feature focused">

      <div class='container'>

        <div class="row row-inverted">
          <div class="col-sm-7">
            <h4 class="i18n">{{_t "Keep the meeting focused on the agenda" }}</h4>
            <p class="i18n">{{_t "Solid will let you know on the time remaining before the end of the meeting and the agenda items that are left incomplete. Record your actions, your decisions and your open issues." }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-5 i18n">
            <img src="images/keep-meeting-focused-en.png" width="204" height="186">
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="feature actionable">

      <div class='container'>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-7">
            <h4 class="i18n">{{_t "Receive actionable minutes right after the meeting" }}</h4>
            <p class="i18n">{{_t "All participants receive a detailed summary of the meeting’s outcomes and also a list of their personal upcoming tasks. After all the meetings, a survey is automatically sent to all participants to get their feedback on the meeting's efficiency." }}</p>
          </div>
